OL,2,MThreadz 'n' Webz
OL,4,E-2.378446191688738,52.04030229363161
OL,6,GWe are a bunch of misfits, herded
OL,7,Gtogether by one fabric crazed lady.
OL,8,GBlending webby nerdy things and
OL,9,Gthready oddball crafts. Step back in
OL,10,Gtime and (cyber) space to 199x dial up
OL,11,Gera to find PC and landline phone fun.
OL,12,GOr perhaps following the strings of
OL,13,Gfate to find weaving, fabric and craft
OL,14,Gmadness. Extremely LGBTQ+ friendly.
OL,15,GMay contain ducks, bats, hackers and
OL,16,Gspiders. With thanks to ECHQ/CuTel for
OL,17,Glandlines and Tekhnē-cal for even more
OL,18,Gthready crafts.
OL,22,D]CEMFFAX: The world at your fingertips\
